                           Buckets: 32768  Batches: 1  Memory Usage: 422kB
                          ->  Hash Join  (cost=183.62..596.62 rows=3251 width=19) (actual time=3.489..11.202 rows=3212 loops=1)
                                Hash Cond: (r.inventory_id = i.inventory_id)
                                ->  Seq Scan on rental r  (cost=0.00..318.72 rows=16472 width=8) (actual time=0.008..2.194 rows=16044 loops=1)
                                ->  Hash  (cost=172.02..172.02 rows=928 width=19) (actual time=3.189..3.189 rows=924 loops=1)
                                       Buckets: 32768  Batches: 1  Memory Usage: 304kB
                                      ->  Hash Join  (cost=69.92..172.02 rows=928 width=19) (actual time=1.080..2.707 rows=924 loops=1)
                                            Hash Cond: (i.film_id = f.film_id)
